"3717-1-05.1(D) - Violation - Backflow prevention-air gap.

The air gap between the water supply and flood level rim of a plumbing fixture (or other equipment) does not meet requirements.  "
violation_comments:
"OBSERVATION: Backflow prevention-air gap.

1-In the dining room, the 2 soda station//ice bins had air gaps that did not meet requirements.  2-The water supply inlet pipe was not correctly aligned to the drain at the ice machine air gap, allowing drain water to accumulate on the floor behind the machine.  
 
CORRECTIVE ACTION: 1-The PIC was instructed to correct these air gapps so they are twice the diameter of the water supply inlet and at least 1"".  2-The PIC was instructed to move the ice machine so that air gaps is better aligned, stopping all water accumuation.  "

There was visible dirt and debris on dry wiping cloths or on wet wiping cloths in a freshly made sanitizing solution."
violation_comments: "Violation has been abated"

violation_description:
"3717-1-02.3(C)  - Violation - Hair restraints,  effectiveness

Food employee(s) did not have their hair effectively restrained."
violation_comments: "Violation has been abated"

violation_description:
"3701-21-02(G) - Violation - Catering License

Caterer operating without obtaining or displaying a catering license from the appropriate board of health."
violation_comments: "Violation has been abated"

violation_description:
"3717-1-05.1(O)(2) - Violation - Using handwashing facility-Other purposes

Handwashing facility is being used for purposes other than handwashing. "
violation_comments: "Violation has been abated"

violation_description:
"3717-1-03.2(C)(2) - Violation - Protection from Contamination-Food Storage

Food is stored unwrapped or in  uncovered containers."
violation_comments: "Violation has been abated"

violation_description:
"3717-1-03.4(C)  - Violation - Thawing TCS-Temperature / Time Control

TCS food was improperly thawed."
violation_comments:
"Thawing TCS-Temperature / Time Control

TCS food was improperly thawed.

Observed frozen hot dogs thawing in stagnate water.

PIC to ensure approved thawing method used."

violation_description:

Ready-to-eat, TCS food was not discarded by the date mark, or was undated and not discarded or was not discarded when the date mark exceeded the required time/temperature combination."
violation_comments: "Violation has been abated"

violation_description:
"3717-1-03.4(I)(1) - Violation - Time as a public health control

Written procedures for time as a public health control improper or unavailable."
violation_comments: "Violation has been abated"

violation_description:
"3717-1-06.4(B)(1) - Violation - Facilities: Cleaning: Frequency 

The physical facilities are not cleaned as often as necessary to keep them clean."
violation_comments: "Violation has been abated"

violation_description:
"3717-1-07.1(A) - Violation - Poisonous/toxic material-storage separation

Poisonous/toxic materials are stored in a manner that could contaminate food, equipment, utensils, linens, or single-service or single-use articles."
violation_comments: "Violation has been abated"
